{"type": "article", "id": 13314, "title": "白瓷洗手盆", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-11T06:50:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002375oEK1ysxizlCANhP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自米兰的两位设计师 niccolò adolini 和 daniel simonini 推出了一款洗手盆，它可以悬挂在墙上，也可以安置在架子上。洗手盆所使用的陶瓷材料看起来干净，而设计上则力求简洁实用。连同这款洗手盆一起推出的还有同样用陶瓷材料制成的 “soft”， “was” 和 “wide” 三件作品，都是为家居品牌 White Ceramic 设计，点击这里可以查看详细信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000235LwyKRiNu9Flbfsj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000235BflLe28yrsaHTYbE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000236vaodZAKbQPWw5Ikg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7603912\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000236nCIy8ZQRtVYsXgTM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93765281\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}